# Payment providers (frozen for i18n)

## For Persian / display Toman work

- **Do not** change provider payment flows, webhook amount logic, or API payloads for “showing Toman”
- **Do not** add inline `/100` or rate hacks in handlers here

## Allowed (narrow)

- **C2C plugin:** user-facing card text + `format_price` in `app/plugins/c2c/` only
- **FX changes:** only under `currency-fx-boundaries.mdc` — one provider per commit series, documented rate

## Internal amounts

YooKassa, Stars, crypto, etc. keep existing integer semantics; user label comes from layer 2 (`format_price`), not from rewriting provider math in this layer.
